main :: IO ()
main = solve <$> f >>= mapM_ B.putStrLn
  where
    f = B.lines <$> B.getContents

solve :: [ByteString] -> [ByteString]
solve = filter f
  where
    f bs = all isNeighbor $ B.zip bs (B.tail bs)

N = 1000
G = 3
GG = G * G

BTNS = ["ABC", "DEF", "GHI"]
DXYS = [[1, 0], [0, 1], [-1, 0], [0, -1]]

### main

nbrs = Array.new(GG){Array.new(GG){false}}

for y0 in (0...G)
  for x0 in (0...G)
    c0 = BTNS[y0][x0].ord - 'A'.ord

    DXYS.each do |dx, dy|
      x = x0 + dx
      y = y0 + dy
      if x >= 0 && x < G && y >= 0 && y < G
        c1 = BTNS[y][x].ord - 'A'.ord
        nbrs[c0][c1] = nbrs[c1][c0] = true
      end
    end
  end
end

while line = gets
  str = line.strip

  cf = true
  prvc = str[0].ord - 'A'.ord

  for i in (1...str.length)
    c = str[i].ord - 'A'.ord
    if ! nbrs[prvc][c]
      cf = false
      break
    end
    prvc = c
  end

  puts str if cf
end

rule = {"A" => ["B", "D"], "B" => ["A", "C", "E"], "C" => ["B", "F"], "D" => ["A", "E", "G"], "E" => ["B", "D", "F", "H"], "F" => ["C", "E", "I"], "G" => ["D", "H"], "H" => ["E", "G", "I"], "I" => ["F", "H"]}
1000.times{
    line = gets.chomp
    candidate = true
    c = line[0]
    1.upto(line.length - 1){|i|
        unless rule[c].include?(line[i])
            candidate = false
            break
        end
        c = line[i]
    }
    puts line if candidate
}
